commit_message:
Initial work for tempest functional test

This patch does some initial work for tempest functional test:
1. BaseSenlinTest is now base class of all Senlin tempest test classes.
   Define BaseSenlinFunctionalTest as base class of all functional test
   classes and BaseSenlinAPITest as base class of all API test classses;
2. Define wait_for_status and wait_for_delete functions in basic client
   class ClusteringAPIClient rather than BaseSenlinTest class;
3. Define ClusteringFunctionalClient for functional test;
4. Remove test/tempest/scenario directory;

Change-Id: Ia2637e4b5cdf2782fbab64f5d5c79641df4958b8
